TY  - JOUR
T1  - Investment in Series and Parallel Systems to Maximize Expected Life
AU  - Jacobsen, S. E.
AU  - Arunkumar, S.
Y1  - 1973/05/01
PY  - 1973
DA  - 1973/05/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.19.9.1023
